{"generated":"2026-03-30T05:18:04.569793966Z","published":"2023-03-22T11:52:56Z","app":"watchexec","version":"1.22.2","notes":"<p dir=\"auto\"><em>Software development often involves running the same commands over and over. Boring! Watchexec is a simple, standalone tool that watches a path and runs a command whenever it detects modifications. Install it today with <a href=\"https://github.com/cargo-bins/cargo-binstall\"><code class=\"notranslate\">cargo-binstall watchexec-cli</code></a>, from the binaries below, find it <a href=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/blob/main/doc/packages.md\">in your favourite package manager</a>, or build it from source with <code class=\"notranslate\">cargo install watchexec-cli</code>.</em></p>\n<h4 dir=\"auto\">In this release:</h4>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li>Paths on windows are normalised to unix format prior to being filtered. Windows-style patterns still work, but unix-style patterns will also now work (better). (<a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"1555381859\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/issues/487\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/watchexec/watchexec/issues/487/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/issues/487\">#487</a>, <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"1634189241\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/issues/546\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/watchexec/watchexec/issues/546/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/issues/546\">#546</a>, <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"1635384761\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/issues/558\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/watchexec/watchexec/pull/558/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/pull/558\">#558</a>)</li>\n<li>Options that would send signals to processes are ignored on Windows, as we don't have support for non-kill signals there. (<a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"1027348988\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/issues/219\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/watchexec/watchexec/issues/219/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/issues/219\">#219</a>, <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"1632734302\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/issues/544\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/watchexec/watchexec/issues/544/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/issues/544\">#544</a>, <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"1635443557\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/issues/559\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/watchexec/watchexec/pull/559/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/pull/559\">#559</a>)</li>\n</ul>","downloads":[{"url":"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/releases/download/v1.22.2/watchexec-1.22.2-aarch64-unknown-linux-gnu.deb","filename":"watchexec-1.22.2-aarch64-unknown-linux-gnu.deb","size":1833448,"format":{"short":"DEB","long":"Debian/Ubuntu package","tool":"dpkg -i"},"sums":[{"algo":"BLAKE3","sum":"b533e05d1a710e9f7a96450e2c28f68b10b74c74eac30c3705965729507f1302"},{"algo":"SHA256","sum":"665eb37f80f9c42022154d353db7135fded90ecceacfdc98bbddcb3857488ac9"},{"algo":"SHA512","sum":"a6502dfc6fe5c18287e2476227e42cbd8eb7776cd34b8c645926948d16c3f9ca9990ace6e0ab01f370ea81dfce4d69e72dc99c34a704ea59c3ff1c4cbbb9e372"}],"cats":["Linux","AArch64"